section.section:
Of the 26 members:
23 members shall be appointed by the Governor upon the recommendation of the Board of Trustees, with the advice and consent of the Senate;
1 member shall be the Chairman of the Historic St. Mary's City Commission, or the Chairman's designee;
1 member shall be the President of the St. Mary's Alumni Association; and
1 member shall be a student in good academic standing at the College.
